~ Start it with : play run project_name
~ Have fun!
~
</code></pre>

<p>動作確認はJavaの時と同様に $ play run [project_name] で出来ます。</p>

<h4>$ play run project_name/</h4>

<pre><code>~        _                _ 
~  _ __ | | __ _ _  _| |
~ | '_ \| |/ _' | || |_|
~ |  __/|_|\____|\__ (_)
~ |_|            |__/   
~
~ play! 1.2.2, http://www.playframework.org
~
